al/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 果時真係嚇死"},{"pid":"aaa020ab659250a90829fc02a2d16b3bcaf81cc3","tid":211344,"uid":100637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T16:34:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>細個偷睇蘋果風月版俾呀爸問我睇馬經做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住我答佢: d馬幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過幾日我見佢開始識拎馬經睇風月版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 真絲 細細個太好奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前真係會趁阿爸阿媽做緊家務偷偷地摷份風月版出黎睇,跟住要係佢地搞掂晒之前攝返入去,好刺激<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我屋企好保守 未見過我老豆老母錫錫<br />\n果陣唔知點解咁夠薑咁多人係廳都拎住份馬經睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94698223db6a3f55b80b3db65195ecdd7f0c7333","tid":211344,"uid":85409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T16:34:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>細個偷睇蘋果風月版俾呀爸問我睇馬經做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住我答佢: d馬幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過幾日我見佢開始識拎馬經睇風月版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 真絲 細細個太好奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前真係會趁阿爸阿媽做緊家務偷偷地摷份風月版出黎睇,跟住要係佢地搞掂晒之前攝返入去,好刺激<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我試過射落d 風月板到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af1d33aa076db971bcf2d74c40e4bb914f275c27","tid":211344,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T16:36:11.000Z","msg":"以為全家出曬去，自己係到扮貓叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccc389092fc0800c33fc88b2b7131dd2378c3080","tid":211344,"uid":7323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T16:38:16